OL,3,CSearches underway after boy gets into
OL,4,Cdifficulty while swimming in river
OL,6,FSearches are underway for a boy after
OL,7,Fit is believed he got into difficulty
OL,8,Fwhile swimming in a river with friends.
OL,10,FLancashire Police say officers were
OL,11,Fcalled to Ribchester, in the Ribble
OL,12,FValley, shortly after 2pm on 26 May
OL,13,Ffollowing reports of concern for the
OL,14,Fwelfare of the child.
OL,16,FA force spokeswoman said: "We were
OL,17,Fcalled at just after 2pm today
OL,18,F(Tuesday) to a concern for the welfare
OL,19,Fof a child who had gone into the river
OL,20,Fat Ribchester.
