OL,3,CSearches underway after boy gets into
OL,4,Cdifficulty while swimming in river
OL,6,F"The child, a boy, had got into
OL,7,Fdifficulty while swimming with friends.
OL,9,F"Emergency services are at the scene
OL,10,Fand searches are ongoing."
OL,12,FMore to follow.
